================================================================================
DEDICATED VIDEO LOOPER FOR RASPI:
================================================================================

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Git - pi_video_looper:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
https://github.com/adafruit/pi_video_looper

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
https://learn.adafruit.com/raspberry-pi-video-looper/installation

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install Commands:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install -y git
git clone https://github.com/adafruit/pi_video_looper.git
cd pi_video_looper
sudo ./install.sh

